Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個兵器擁有打破世界的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將世界引同滅亡的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像巴哈姆特一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱緊我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去神界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得故鄉的奶奶說過以前經常去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 去妮娜的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.85,0:01:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稟報
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越獄的貞德·達克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.81,0:01:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法瓦羅·雷歐涅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜·朵蘭格的行蹤目前還未查到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.07,0:01:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多目擊情報
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神秘的小孩的情況也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已對凱撒·利德法爾德進行過拷問了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過他什麼都設說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是奧爾良騎士團的團長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多練練再來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越獄犯就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:01:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去艾博斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人要見你 起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄亞思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牢房生活已經步入正軌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起鐵欄杆 你還是更適合握劍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士團情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.01,0:04:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,團長都被抓了 還能怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄亞思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾良騎士團就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,團長是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我見到貞德大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她還是一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾良騎士團必將復活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要讓騎士團跟貞德大人一起重獲榮光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給貞德大人和我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能直接叫妮娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿姨 妮娜回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是莫拉 叫瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何叫瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回來啦 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我朋友 貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在王都流行這種衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要丟下你囉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來啦 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我故鄉的奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是貞德...達克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不是擺設哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 你變瘦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我朋友貞德說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何都要去神界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 你去過神界的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我們怎麼去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你啦 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝嗎 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那什麼...自便
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2000年前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神與惡魔齊心協力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹掉了巴哈姆特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時背著精疲力盡的神明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.79,0:09:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將他們送回神界的正是老朽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.54,0:09:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來啦 又是這一段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是我當年的英姿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何 帥氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是迷上老朽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這背 怎麼坐嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不理你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 生氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無論如何都要去神界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還望您助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡著了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 睡著就叫不醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡的溫泉可厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又能療傷 還能去除疲勞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶吶 貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽羅妹妹的爸爸帥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊 貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人不是你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還叫那位大人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟戀爰不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 小孩不是愛的結晶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人 如今仍在守護著我和艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.22,0:11:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有傾心的男性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要接近帥氣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.94,0:12:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會變成龍大鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此一直無法跟傾心的人好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 唯獨能跟那人一起跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要跟他在一起就很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至覺得我來到世上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是為了跟他跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是初戀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.05,0:12:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.84,0:12:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德的初戀是怎樣的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在春心萌動之前就收到了啟示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以神的僕人的身份上戰場了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神的僕人不能戀愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但願妮娜能跟那人過上幸福的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我最討厭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我也不知道該怎麼辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明人超好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然做了那麼多可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.18,0:13:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此仍然喜歡他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此我依然無法恨他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我心中也有多個面目各異的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有兩張相反的面目也不足為奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:14:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果妮娜能愛上他的所有面目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份戀情也許就是真愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德 真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.27,0:14:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好看得很 好看得很
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜要待多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要去趟神界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神界？我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不是說去就去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.34,0:15:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去神界幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去見姆伽羅妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽羅妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽羅妹妹是貞德的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是失散的神聖之子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神聖之子？什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,編吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家就是知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神聖之子就是神聖之子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是問你神聖之子是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡不著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝水的話 那裡有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的話 要聊幾句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是個很神奇的村子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次來也很震驚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我不是龍族來著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山腳的村子出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是嫁過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜真是個好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊 寄養在我們家的孩子們的父母畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個村子的日子也不好過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都出去賺錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜的父親也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子的父親已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前 為了保護村子不被火球砸中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒能逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子有沒有突然變龍你們添麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 她救了我們的命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 那孩子也長大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.57,0:17:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她自從父親死的那天開始就變了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.58,0:17:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要靠近跟她父親年紀相仿的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會變成龍大鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:18:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不去回想痛苦的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.64,0:18:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你當她的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這人根本不值得感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對妮娜的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要看過她有多親近你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道你對妮娜有多好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.25,0:18:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要說謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:18:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都叫你收斂點了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刻耳子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這時候就該說那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是團長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再大聲點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是團長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要娶你當團長夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點啊 團長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 副團長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是奧爾良騎士團的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我不就開個玩笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生什麼氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 刻耳子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆睡好沒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡得可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想來也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真打算去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 要怎麼去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了 坐我背上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你那小身板...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.93,0:20:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會帶著天使回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.61,0:21:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 路上當心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好保護貞德哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.42,0:23:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能撐多久
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就突破極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.77,0:23:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德 你擅長什麼料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼突然提起這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅長什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.94,0:23:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.77,0:23:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 神擊的巴哈姆特 Virgin Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.02,0:23:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神之都 P1
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.69,0:23:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅長什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:23:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.07,0:23:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用湯煮菜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.95,0:24:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是湯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還望下集繼續關照
